WEBVTT

1
02:53:42.430 --> 02:53:43.670 
真是个好消息
Well, that's good news.

2
02:53:44.710 --> 02:53:46.590 
那萨鲁曼呢
And what about Saruman?

3
02:53:46.820 --> 02:53:48.780 
你们商量的结果是什么
Have you come to a decision about him?

4
02:53:49.800 --> 02:53:53.210 
不要着急  梅里雅达克先生
Now, don't be hasty, Master Meriadoc.

5
02:53:53.490 --> 02:53:54.720 
不着急
Hasty?

6
02:53:55.870 --> 02:53:57.410 
我们的朋友正在浴血奋战
Our friends are out there.

7
02:53:57.630 --> 02:53:59.730 
需要我们的帮助
They need our help.

8
02:53:59.940 --> 02:54:01.920 
孤军奋战死路一条
They cannot fight this war on their own.

9
02:54:02.390 --> 02:54:04.380 
战争吗  没错
War? Yes.

10
02:54:04.760 --> 02:54:06.630 
战争会影响我们
It affects us all.

11
02:54:06.860 --> 02:54:09.700 
树干  树根  树枝
Tree, root and twig.

